 《Helldivers 2》挑逗第三派系供玩家战斗https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/helldivers-2-teases-third-faction-for-players-to-fight-3589967?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=helldivers-2-teases-third-玩家战斗的派系Imogen DonovanTue, 20 Feb 2024 11:14:35 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3589967 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Helldivers 2：可以看到几名士兵在射击虫子。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这可能是最初的“Helldivers”外星人之一的回归</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/helldivers-2-teases-third-faction-for-players-to-fight-3589967">《Helldivers 2》的帖子挑逗了供玩家战斗的第三派系，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Helldivers 2：可以看到几名士兵在射击虫子。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-xbox-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/arrowhead-game-studios">Arrowhead Game Studios</a>似乎在游戏内关于“照亮目击事件”的公告中暗示<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/helldivers-2"><em>《Helldivers 2》</em></a>玩家将有第三个派系进行战斗。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/soren-lundgaard-ghost-ship-games-deep-rock-galactic-3586886">Søren Lundgaard 如何消除电子游戏的毒性</a></strong></li></ul><p>照亮者出现在科幻射击游戏系列的第一部作品中。作为一个极其先进的外星种族，他们利用自己的认知能力创建了一个监视和技术网络，以探索太空并了解敌人的情况。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.theloadout.com/helldivers-2/illuminate-third-faction" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Loadout》</em></a>报道，游戏中的一艘船广播形式的复活节彩蛋提到了“照明目击事件的谣言”，这被归结为“持不同政见者的作品”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3588639" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588639" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588639" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release.jpg" alt="《Helldivers 2》PS4：可以看到一个人投掷手榴弹" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-ps4-release-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588639" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：箭头游戏工作室</figcaption></figure><p>目前， <em>《Helldivers 2》的</em>战斗对象是机器人或终结者，需要不同的策略来对付他们的不同方法。</p><p>自动机的防御主要集中在装甲上，并且它们可以通过远程攻击保持在火线之外。然而，它们很容易受到玩家的能量武器和穿甲攻击。另一方面，终结者以近战策略涌入战场，但它们的火力较弱。</p><p>目前尚不清楚可能的光明派系将如何发挥作用，但在<em>《Helldivers》中，</em>不被外星人巡逻队发现很重要。然后销毁信标，然后阻止了照明的人发出警报并堆放在球员队伍上，以确保战斗保持公平。</p><p>由于Arrowhead Game Studios没有关于Illuminate在<em>Helldivers 2</em>的潜在到来的消息，因此玩家可能会等待一段时间才能正式确认。 </p><figure id="attachment_3584983" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3584983" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3584983" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join.jpg" alt="《地狱潜水员 2》：在一个星球上可以看到多个地狱潜水员" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/helldivers-2-failed-to-join-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3584983" class="wp-caption-text">学分：索尼互动娱乐</figcaption></figure><p>本周早些时候，开发人员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/helldivers-2-makes-its-hardest-mission-easier-in-latest-update-3589568">为游戏推出了一个新的补丁</a>，这减少了其最艰难的任务的困难。此外，在发射过程中困扰着数千名玩家的服务器问题继续解决。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，任天堂的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/a-nintendo-direct-partner-showcase-will-air-tomorrow-3589932">下一个任天堂直接合作伙伴展示明天将播出</a>，粉丝们想知道PC和Xbox系列X/S独家<em>Hi-Fi Rush</em>是否会露面。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/helldivers-2-teases-third-faction-for-players-to-fight-3589967">“ Helldivers 2”帖子嘲笑第三个派系，让玩家战斗</a>是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现的。</p> ;
